snippet.title: OUTLAWED | First Official Trailer
snippet.description:
OUTLAWED is a crime-themed PvPvE first-person extraction shooter, set in a modern city overrun by gangs. Enter solo or with a squad to challenge powerful enemies and search for riches, and use everything at your disposal to make it out alive.

Wishlist now on Steam：
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3193840/

Join our Discord Server：
https://discord.gg/zCaH4CKdmP

Follow us on X:
https://x.com/OutlawedGame
